items.name: Garmin Vivofit Fitness Band, Available in multiple colors
items.categoryPath: Sports & Outdoors/Exercise & Fitness/Exercise & Fitness Accessories/Stretch Bands & Cords
items.shortDescription: With the Garmin Vivofit Fitness Band, getting in shape and meeting your daily fitness goals are much easier. It greets you with your personalized fitness goal, helps you track your progress and reminds you when it's time to move. This colored Garmin fitness band displays your steps along with a countdown to the goal you've set for yourself to help you stay motivated. It also shows the calories you've burned and the distance you've traveled on its easy-to-read display, along with the time. You can pair this Vivofit band with a heart-rate monitor to keep track of that data during your workouts, runs and other fitness activities. The band is also water-resistant to help it stand up to inclement weather and perspiration. In addition, it provides you with access to Garmin Connect, where you can take part in challenges, save and share your progress and more. The Garmin Vivofit Fitness Band makes getting in shape more enjoyable.

items.name: Fitbit Zip Wireless Act Tracker
items.shortDescription: The Fitbit Zip Wireless Act Tracker is an efficient way to monitor your everyday fitness. Its versatile functionality provides you with detailed feedback so you can easily stay on track. Much more than a pedometer, this Fitbit Zip activity tracker records your steps, distance traveled and calories burned, and it automatically syncs the data to your account through your computer. It can also be used with select smartphones and tablets. Whether you are online or using the Fitbit app, you can use this wireless fitness tracker to set goals and stay motivated to keep on your path to fitness with graphs and congratulatory badges. It enables you to see how you compare with friends and family for mutual goals or even friendly competition. The Fitbit Zip Wireless Act Tracker is designed to withstand sweat, rain and splashes. It's powered by a three-volt lithium-ion battery.

items.name: Fitbit Aria Wi-Fi Smart Scale
items.shortDescription: <p>The Fitbit Aria Wi-Fi Smart Scale measures your weight, body fat percentage and body mass index (BMI) to provide a full picture of your weight management trends. This Wi-Fi-enabled scale helps you reach your weight goals by letting you set goals, track your progress effortlessly and stay motivated each and every day. Your stats automatically upload to your Fitbit dashboard through Wi-Fi, where you can get a more comprehensive view of your health and fitness and track your eating and exercise habits. This black Fitbit Aria smart scale is ideal if you want a way to track your fitness progress over a long period of time. It's comprehensive graphs chart out weight, body fat percentage and body mass index over time and will help you reach your fitness goals efficiently. Whether you're trying to bulk up or slim down, you'll be able to track small changes each day to see clear trends over a period of time.</p>
items.longDescription: <b>Fitbit Aria Wi-Fi Smart Scale, Black:</b><ul><li>Measures weight, body fat percentage and body mass index (BMI)</li><li>Wi-fi body fat scale lets you set goals, track progress and stay motivated</li><li>Stats automatically upload to your Fitbit dashboard through Wi-Fi</li><li>Scale can be set up to automatically recognize up to 8 users</li><li>Check your progress from computer or free smartphone app</li><li>Available in two colors: Black or White</li></ul>

items.name: Fitbit One Wireless Act Tracker
items.shortDescription: Fitness means being active, sleeping well and eating smarter - and the Fitbit One Wireless Activity Tracker helps you do all three. During the day, it tracks your steps taken, distance walked, calories burned and stairs climbed. During the night it measures your sleep cycle to help you see how to sleep better, and it can even wake you in the morning without waking your partner. Your stats upload wirelessly from the Fitbit Pedometer via computer or select mobile devices (like the iPhone 4S), making it easy to keep track of your progress. Powered by your stats, it can help you set goals and monitor progress with charts and graphs to stay on track with your health and fitness regimen. The Fitbit One Wireless Activity Tracker can also help you stay motivated by letting you earn badges or connecting you with friends for support or friendly competitions. Log food, workouts and more. Bring greater fitness into your life seamlessly, socially, 24 hours a day<br>

items.name: Fitbit Flex Wireless Wristband
items.shortDescription: <p>Get motivated with the Fitbit Flex Wireless Activity Band. This slim device can be worn all the time and be used to help track your movements. Use it to track the number of steps taken each day as well as the number of calories burned. Set daily goals and then check to see how you are stacking up. The Fitbit Flex black band can even be worn at night. It will track your sleep cycle and help you learn how to sleep better. It will silently wake you in the morning when it is time to get up. Access the data compiled by the Fitbit Flex band whenever you want from a computer, tablet or smartphone. It is compatible with both iPhone and Android devices for easy access to information. The band is water resistant so it can be worn outside even if it is raining or snowing. This band is a companion that can stay with you all the time and go with you wherever you go.</p>

With integrated GPS and automatic, continuous, wrist-based heart rate tracking, this fitness watch gives you real-time workout stats like pace, distance, calories burned, heart rate intensity and target zones to make the most of your training. The Fitbit Surge Black watch also lets you stay connected on the move with advanced smartwatch features like call and text notifications and music control. With this accessory, you'll make every moment count. It's available in multiple sizes and is water-resistant.
